parameters.name: Accept
parameters.description: The data format of the response. The value must be application/x-protobuf.

parameters.name: Accept-Encoding
parameters.description: The compression format of the response. The value can be lz4.

parameters.name: body
parameters.description: The format of the response parameters. The value is \`protobuf\`.

parameters.description: The idempotency token for the request.
